{"tid":2422473,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真的要發SOLO了嗎？BLACKPINK ROSÉ出演《我家的熊孩子》特別MC，預計在3月中播出！","createTime":"2021-02-25T08:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:08:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"390efbb2234c32b48f9dd12eb030b4a5a81e06f4","tid":2422473,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_6cef0ed34ce8b4a3317b0731d97b3ea4/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-25/133892-898014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_6cef0ed34ce8b4a3317b0731d97b3ea4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-25%2F133892-898014.jpg&h=912e76f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始錄綜藝了，應該也快要發行SOLO專輯了吧！<br />\n<br />\n今日（25日），SBS方面表示：「BLACKPINK ROS&Eacute;擔任《我家的熊孩子》特別MC，最近結束了錄製，預計在3月中旬播出。」而ROS&Eacute;作爲最年少特別MC與大家見面，會與出演者的母親們聊什麼樣的話題，也備受關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8118e8f1f2e0a01d7e149d1bea1b1875/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-25/133892-898005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8118e8f1f2e0a01d7e149d1bea1b1875%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-25%2F133892-898005.jpg&h=87f72d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖：YG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK成員ROS&Eacute;在上月31日舉行的線上演唱會《THE SHOW》公開SOLO曲《GONE》。YG當時也表示：「ROS&Eacute;的SOLO專輯主打歌MV拍攝已全部結束，由於投入歷代級製作費、規模也很大，為了提高完整度，正在盡全力進行後期工作。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e4ae6cde32f887bda08a218c03878313/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-25/133892-898003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e4ae6cde32f887bda08a218c03878313%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-25%2F133892-898003.jpg&h=db27a801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_be84328fae30b57f0b3a58533965a406/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-25/133892-898010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_be84328fae30b57f0b3a58533965a406%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-25%2F133892-898010.jpg&h=85d0d500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：IG@roses_are_rosie）<br />\n<br />\n她的SOLO預告影片在上月25日公開，僅僅33秒卻讓人忍不住重複播放，歌詞唱著：「我的愛已逝去，我的愛已逝去，而你也跟著在我心裡消亡。」目前點擊已經突破4300萬，相信粉絲們都很期待吧？也希望YG可以快點公告相關消息啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e9ed1c2402549203e9fc25b9a97a4650/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-25/133892-898004.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e9ed1c2402549203e9fc25b9a97a4650%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-25%2F133892-898004.png&h=fdbb17c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9e808965bf208c893bb5baf89d18872d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-25/133892-898006.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9e808965bf208c893bb5baf89d18872d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-25%2F133892-898006.png&h=9464b90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：YouTube@BLACKPINK截圖）"},{"pid":"2fae3d6d5024b4efa953454e124ad6fa0ffe37ee","tid":2422473,"uid":58512,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"早就要啦<br />\n唱歌屌打其餘個3隻臭雞"},{"pid":"5d441983680c97f11690ed936d15347bb8e5e6c1","tid":2422473,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fae3d6d5024b4efa953454e124ad6fa0ffe37ee","tid":2422473,"uid":58512,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"早就要啦<br />\n唱歌屌打其餘個3隻臭雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"米話人臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f1391af0806c472df6c25535295705b84ea965","tid":2422473,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2fae3d6d5024b4efa953454e124ad6fa0ffe37ee","tid":2422473,"uid":58512,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"早就要啦<br